info.description:
This package provides a simple but efficient least-recently-used
(LRU) cache module. A single class, LRUCache, with a container
interface, provides prioritized caching. The implementation uses a
heap and a dictionary to provide quick inserts, deletes, and
references.
info.name: lrucache
